STEPS TO CREATE AN APPLICATION :

Step No 3: Login Page (Enter your credential to login)
1. Open Developer Console
2. File ---> New ---> Select Apex Class(enter name to apex class and save Clt+s)
3.Type below mentioned code
    public class pract3 { 
        public Double myValue = 0; 
        public Double get() {
            myValue = myValue+10;
            return myValue;
        }
    }

4. Click on Debug ---> Open Execute Acronymous Window

5. Type below code(Apex Code)
pract3 m=new pract3();
Double Value=m.get();
system.debug('valued='+Value);

6. Click on Open log then Execute code

7. Click on Debug only (You will get output)